{"tid":2188523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潔篪訪西班牙晤首相桑切斯　強調要共同維護多邊主義","createTime":"2020-09-04T09:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T11:21:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6c1d02f40c81f3f8d6c8577d3e0c5c340932eb","tid":2188523,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"西班牙首相桑切斯在馬德里會見到訪的中共中央政治局委員、中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪。<br />\n<br />\n楊潔篪表示，要共同維護多邊主義，維護國際公平正義，推動完善全球治理，相信西班牙方面將繼續為促進中歐關係發展發揮建設性作用。<br />\n<br />\n楊潔篪又說，雙方要保持高層交往，鞏固政治互信，繼續相互支持彼此核心利益和重大關切，要擴大雙邊投資貿易，中方願意進口更多西班牙農產品。<br />\n<br />\n桑切斯表示，西班牙願意進一步拓展中國市場，也歡迎中國企業到西班牙投資。西班牙、歐盟和中國都堅定支持多邊主義，要加強溝通協調。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547744-20200904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547744-20200904.htm&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c66bb2b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547744-20200904.htm&h=a5b15a2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547744-20200904.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0c5f1adbe5efd39fd41e2d099dc33d662085d10","tid":2188523,"uid":276548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"多你老母邊咩支共<br />\n全球抗支係共識黎"},{"pid":"b86183b505de1d3f88482bbde6cd9d1ca80d7145","tid":2188523,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"比美帝打緊既時候要多邊主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係南海蝦蝦霸霸既時候要單邊主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79199e887eb0f755e9d47ebfcab13934cf72f39a","tid":2188523,"uid":297436,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"加泰集會係一場贏左無得分，輸左死全家既賭局<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akzrCOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akzrCOU</a><b